edu.cmu.tetrad.data

Interface IKnowledge

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable, TetradSerializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Knowledge, Knowledge2

    public interface IKnowledge
extends TetradSerializable
    Interface for knowledge of forbidden and required edges. Implemented in different ways. See implementations.
